M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, aqenduṛ wis sin anagar uɣen luḍu. ?ṭfen daɣen deg waṭas n lɛaddat nniḍen : tarda n yeqbac, n tbuqalin, akk-d lḥilat meṛṛa n nnḥas.
Ayen akk i d-iqqimen seg umeslay-ik, akukru i s-d-yefka Sidi Ṛebbi : Di yal taswiɛt, s yiwet n teswiɛt kan, sserriḥ-ed aṭas n tikkal.
Llan aṭas n leṣnaf n tukciwin n Ṛebbi, mkul yiwen d acu i gzemren ad afen tamɛict-nsen.
Ur ilaq ara a d-nini xlut ixxamen-nwen iwakken aț-țejbed ayen s wayes ara tfehmem, lameɛna ilaq a t-id-yedṛu ula d ayen i gewɛed Sidi Ṛebbi.
Sefhayen iheddeṛ aṭas n tutlayin ur nețwassen ara, lameɛna am akken yura di tektabt n ?abur :
Asirem-agi d ayen yeṭṭfen tudert-nneɣ am umextaf ( tnejga ) yeṭṭfen lbabuṛ, yețɛedday akkin i leḥjab ɣer wemkan iqedsen,
Ssufella n usenduq-agi rsent snat n lmeṣnuɛat imetlen lmalayekkat, ɣumment s tili n wafriwen-nsent amkan-nni i țṛuccun s idammen n iseflawen i leɛfu n ddnubat.
Sufella n usenduq-agi rsent snat n lmeṣnuɛat imetlen lmalayekkat, ɣumment s tili n wafriwen-nsent amkan-nni i țṛuccun s idammen n iseflawen i leɛfu n ddnubat.
daymi i gefhem ayen i d-yenna tura, init-ed kan akken ilaq, aț-țissineḍ annect-agi i leǧnas nniḍen. S wakka ițbeggin-ed s waṭas n lɛaddat-nsen.
Lameɛna atan wayen i ɣef ara tweṣṣiḍ s tutlayt ur nețwassen ara, deg-sen daɣen ara ad slemden ayen i d-ițbegginen belli d ajlili i gella.
Lameɛna m'ara bdunt fessunt, qṛib ad yaweḍ ɣer tmezduɣt n tmurt n Sbanya, qṛib ad yaweḍ ɣer tmezduɣt-nni, ad tbedd ɣer tmurt n Sbanya.
Uqbel a d-yas lweqt i deg ara sen-d-yefk Sidi Ṛebbi ṛṛeḥma i wid ara yilin di lexla, wid ara yilin d sebba n tuccḍa, ma d wiyaḍ a ten-id-yerr ɣer webrid.
Yiwen wass deg ussan-nni, leḥsab n widak yumnen s Sidna Ɛisa yețzid irennu. At Isṛail i d-yusan si tmura nniḍen, yețmeslayen s tyunanit, ccetkan ɣef wat Isṛail, axaṭer m'ara feṛqen lmakla, ur d-țelhayen ara ț-țuǧǧal-nsen.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Walit acḥal meqqeṛ ccan n win iwumi yefka Sidna Ɛisa leɛcuṛ seg wayen i d-yerbeḥ deg umenɣi.
Yefka lameṛ, yewwi-d si temdint n Sinya ; anda akken tella yiwen leɛyuba n temdint n Lud.
Di temdint n Jafa, ameqqran n tejmaɛt i d-yețțilin d afarizi, ḥemmlen ad țsellimen fell-asen yemdanen di leswaq, ad ṭṭfen imukan imezwura di tmeɣṛa akk-d Izimer.
Akken daɣen ula d kečč aț-țzerɛeḍ seg wakal, m'ara d-imɣuḍ iman-ik melmi ara s-yernun yid-ek m'ara d-yuɣ lḥal iwakken aț-țesɛuḍ yiwen uɛeqqa n yired.
Ma yella daɣen ț-țiṭ-ik ara k-yawin ɣer ddnub, qleɛ-iț ḍeggeṛ-iț akkin fell-ak ; axiṛ-ik aț-țiliḍ di ddunit s yiwet n tiṭ wala aț-țesɛuḍ leqdeṛ.
Tețțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi yesɛan tazmert tazmert ad iheggin iman-is tameqqrant, daymi i gefṛeḥ aṭas ara t-yawin ɣer wanda ara t-id-yefk. Acḥal yelha m'ara nwali ma d wamek ara t-teččiḍ kullec.
Aṭas n sebbat i gqeḍɛen zzwaǧ i wemdan. Llan wid i d-ilulen si tɛebbuṭ n tmes, kunwi daɣen tmenɛem-t-id acebbak-nneɣ, tețṛuḥum ɣer tama nniḍen, ma d lweqt i deg ara tedṛu d usigna.
Zzin-as-d aṭas n lbeṛhanat i s-ițbecciṛ ɣef temdint n Babilun, ț-țamezduɣt n ccwaṭen, ț-țamezduɣt n wayen yuran di tira iqedsen :t ț-țamezduɣt n Ibṛahim, Isḥaq, Yeɛqub akk-d tilawin n Haǧi.
Taqsiṭ-agi tesɛa lmeɛna nniḍen : tzemrem a d-tinim : Ad ṛuḥen ɣer weksum n temdint n Babilun, mačči d kečč i gețmeslay lameɛna ɣer tmurt n Yahuda yellan di lexṣaṣ, lameɛna armi d ass n temdalen ț-țamurt n Gumuṛ.
A d-tbanent licaṛat deg iṭij, ilaq a d-tban acḥal meqqṛit liman-nsent.
Di tlemmast n ubṛaḥ n temdint tella ttejṛa n tudert iwumi d-yezzi wasif tețțak-ed wuzzal deg yiwet n tbuciḍant, ɣeṛqent, tessalay-ed lemwaji ɣer yiwet n tegzirt.
Ajṛad-nni yecba iɛewdiwen iheggan i umenɣi, sɛan ɣef yiqeṛṛay nsen am akken ț-țiɛeṣṣabin n ddheb,
Axaṭer Tafaska n izimer n leslak tqeṛb-ed seg wass amezwaru. Tameddit n wass uqbel ass n lɛid n Lmasiḥ.
Kunwi ur neḍhiṛ ara di tmurt n Yahuda ț-țigejdit i gellan di tmurt n Lmasiḥ, aṭas n wid ur nelli ara seg wat Isṛail i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, ur nessin ara Sidi Ṛebbi.
Yella wayen i d-ibeggnen annect agi, axaṭer yeffeɣ-ed yiwen n yiḍ di lɛid n Tfaska, bɣan a d-kksen ṭṭlam iwakken ad yali yiṭij.
Tqeṛṛbem ɣer tejmaɛt n wid yextaṛ Ṛebbi d imezwura yesɛan ismawen-nsen uran deg wawal n Ṛebbi. Tqeṛṛbem ɣer Ṛebbi nețța i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi iwakken a d-terreḍ ddehn-ik ɣuṛ-es, isselmad-iten.
Tqeṛṛbem ɣer tejmaɛt n wid yextaṛ Ṛebbi d imezwura yesɛan isɛeddan Tafaska n izimer n leslak. Tameddit n Tfaska țnaṣfa n wass uqbel ass n westeɛfu. Tameddit n wass uqbel ass n lɛid n wass uqbel a d-nekteṛ.
Ayen akk i d-iqqimen di lexla, yekka-d s ujelkaḍ neɣ lewḥuc.
M'ara bdunt fessunt, ur zmiren ara a d-awin lewqam n lebḥeṛ ; ɣas akken qṛib a d-yeǧǧ ad țesriḥ, yenger rrif n lebḥeṛ di tmurt n Jabagus, wagi d ccɣel-nsen.
Seg wasmi i d-texleq ddunit werǧin nesli s idammen n iɛejmiyen d iqelwacen akk-d yiɣed n tgenduzt yeṛɣan d asfel țṣeffin ɣlayen, idɣaɣen n lyaman n mkul ṣṣenf akk-d ddheb,
Ma yebɣa yiwen a nezzenz agummaḍ i lebḥeṛ neɣ agummaḍ i lebḥeṛ, ulac a ț-ijeṛṛeb, axaṭer yebɣa a d-yaf tafat n yiṭij iwakken a t-iɛeddi.
A wen-yessali ɣer yiwet n tɣuṛfeț tameqqrant iwesɛen, kullec yella deg-s. Dinna ara theggim imensi n Tfaska, neɣ m'ulac allen-nsen ad awḍen ɣer lqaɛa.
Imi acḥal teṭṭfem di ddunit meṛṛa, acḥal i sen-yewɛeṛ : yewɛeṛ ɣer lmeqṣud-agi ur țțafen ara ayen n diri ara hedṛen fell-aneɣ yerna ad nneḥcamen.
Leḥjab n wemkan iqedsen n lxiṛ i wen-d-yekkan s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi, lameɛna d leḥjab yellan di tmurt n Yahuda.
D lbaṭel zerɛen ara d-megren, țțafen lfeṛḥ-nsen mi xeddmen ɛinani lebɣi n tnefsit-nsen. Sčuṛen d lɛib akk-d lḥecma, yerna m' ara qqimen yid-wen ɣer lmakla, ur țsetḥin ara s lehduṛ-nsen d ukellex-nsen.
S tideț m'ara ɣ-țṛebbin yețɣiḍ aɣ lḥal lameɛna m'ara tɛeddi teswiɛt-nni, a naf belli d ayen yelhan i tudert-nneɣ.
ilaq ad yeṭṭef deg awal n Sidi Ṛebbi yellan ț-țideț akken i t-yelmed, yerna ad yizmir ad isselmed, ad inhu wiyaḍ yerna a d-isbeggen i wid i d-yekkaten deg awal-agi, belli ɣelṭen.
